Name: Honeysuckle Cake
AttributesDescription: Increases ATK and Crit. DMG of all Resonators in the team by 8% and 12% respectively, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: A cake filled with honeysuckle paste, offering a subtle floral aroma and a distinctly sweet taste.
